6","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25435,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/20\/my-wife-aisha-invited-too\/","url_meta":{"origin":14251,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: Is my wife Aisha invited to dinner, too?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 20, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, had a Persian neighbour who would make good soup. He made some for the Prophet and then came to invite him. The Prophet said, \u201cAnd this is my wife, Aisha.\u201d The man said no, so the Prophet said\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/28\/salat-al-fajr-khayr-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":14251,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Sunan prayer of Fajr better than world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTwo cycles of prayer\u00a0before the dawn\u00a0prayer are better than the world and everything in it. They are both more beloved to me than the entire world.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 725 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7736,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/aisha-khadija-jealous-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14251,"position":3},"title":"Aisha on Khadijah: I was never jealous of any woman like Khadijah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Urwah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \"I never felt so jealous about any woman as I did for Khadijah. She had died three years before I married the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. I heard him mentioning her so often, and his Lord ordered\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15419,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/gabriel-greet-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":14251,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jibreel: Angel Gabriel greets you with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to her, \u201cO Aisha, here is the Angel Gabriel to greet you with peace.\" Aisha said, \"And upon him be peace, the mercy of Allah, and His blessings. You see what I do not see.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6249,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"